products.title: Gibson Home Rockaway 12-Piece Dinnerware Set Service for 4, Grey Matte -
features: Voted "Best Overall Dinnerware Set of 2022" by Better Homes and Gardens
WHAT’S IN THE BOX: Service for 4 that includes 4 of each of the following: 10.5” Dinner Plates, 8” Dessert Plates, 6” (26.5 OZ) Bowls
CARE INSTRUCTIONS: beautiful dishes that are also microwave and dishwasher safe

STONEWARE/MATTE GLAZE: a smooth, flat finish dipped in beautiful solid color creates a sleek and artistic addition to the table. The high firing temperature, thick build, and mix of all-natural clays, makes stoneware an incredibly durable material.

STYLISH DESIGN: a modern simplicity with an off-white edge along the rim brings style into every kitchen. These plates will make a statement. The coupe-shaped edges allow for a stackable and space saving benefit.

FAMILY OWNED: Gibson Homewares is an industry-leading producer of tabletop and housewares products based in Los Angeles, California. Family-owned for over 40 years, we’ve developed a family of brands that include Martha Stewart, Sur La Table, Crock-Pot, Babish, Spice by Tia Mowry, Kenmore, Oster, and more that thrive off relentless commitment to style, innovation, and value for our consumers around the world.
GIBSON HOME: made for everyday living, Gibson Home delivers table and kitchen essentials, with fashion and function, at the best value
products.description: The Gibson Home Rockaway collection gives you a smooth serene matte finish on stoneware with an eggshell edge completing the soft presentation. The coupe shape gives you a generous surface to show off your culinary masterpieces. Service for 4 with a modern cool look. Includes: 4 - 10.5 Inch Dinner Plates 4 - 8 Inch Dessert Plates 4 - 6 Inch Bowls
